{
    "coverpage": {
        "prefix": "cover",
        "scope": "markdown",
        "body": [
            "::: cover",
            "$0",
            ":::"
        ]
    },
    "description": {
        "prefix": "description",
        "scope": "markdown",
        "body": [
            "\"\"\"description",
            "$0",
            "\"\"\""
        ]
    },
    "note": {
        "prefix": "note",
        "scope": "markdown",
        "body": [
            "\"\"\"note",
            "$0",
            "\"\"\""
        ]
    },
    "abilityBlock": {
        "prefix": "abilities",
        "scope": "markdown",
        "body": [
            "{abilities: STR=$1, DEX=$2, CON=$3, INT=$4, WIS=$5, CHA=$6}"
        ]
    },
    "classTable": {
        "prefix": "class",
        "scope": "markdown",
        "body": [
            "::: classtable",
            "##### ${1:Class}",
            "| Level | Proficiency Bonus | Features |",
            "|:-----:|:-----------------:|:--------:|",
            "|  1st  |         +2        | Ability  |",
            ":::"
        ]
    },
    "statBlock": {
        "prefix": "statblock",
        "scope": "markdown",
        "body": [
            ":::stats",
            "## ${1:Name}",
            "*Size Type (subtype), alignment*",
            "___",
            "- **Armor Class** ${2:AC}",
            "- **Hit Points** ${3:HP} (1d8 + 2)",
            "- **Speed** 30 ft.",
            "___",
            "{abilities: STR=10, DEX=10, CON=10, INT=10, WIS=10, CHA=10}",
            "___",
            "- **Senses**",
            "- **Languages** Common",
            "___",
            "- **Ability.** Description.",
            "___",
            "### Actions",
            "- ***Weapon.*** *Melee Weapon Attack:* +2 to hit, reach 5 ft., one target. *Hit:* 4 (1d4 + 2) slashing damage.",
            ":::"
        ]
    }
}